00:07.000 --> 00:11.960
week in connection with the general subject of civil rights. Some of them in the Senate

00:11.960 --> 00:17.200
of the United States, but perhaps the most significant occurred in Knoxville, Tennessee,

00:17.200 --> 00:22.240
