00:22.240 --> 00:27.920
lot about it on the floor of the Senate this week, undoubtedly had its effect on the discussions

00:27.920 --> 00:32.280
on the floor of the Senate and elsewhere in the nation. As you know, there has been

00:32.280 --> 00:38.440
much loose talk these days about southern juries would not conflict those charged with violating

00:38.440 --> 00:43.520
